text: Sarah Walsh (born March 23, 1981) is an American rugby union player. She played for the United States women's national rugby union team at the 2014 Women's Rugby World Cup. She played for Colby College and Berkeley All Blues W.R.C. == References == == Other websites == * Being an Eagle: Sarah Walsh USAWomenEaglesWNT Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:American rugby union players
